HEADWORD: Eraser
<hw>E*ras"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, erases; esp., a sharp instrument or a piece of rubber used to
erase writings, drawings, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
